  <h1>How to Lower Your BMI — Practical, Science-Backed Tips</h1>
  <div class="meta">Last updated: July 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7 min read</div>

  <p>If your BMI is above the healthy range, you are not alone — and more importantly, it is something you can change. Lowering your BMI does not require extreme diets or punishing exercise routines. It requires a consistent, sustainable approach that creates a modest calorie deficit while preserving muscle mass.</p>

